object.customQuery:
Select 
c.SystemId,
c.ParentId,
c.CMMContainer,
c.Id,
c.Status,
c.CoverageCd,
c.FullTermAmt,
c.FullTermManualAmt,
c.WrittenPremiumAmt,
c.FinalPremiumAmt,
c.EarnedAmt,
c.AdditionalInd,
c.OriginalCommissionPct,
c.CommissionPct,
c.ContributionPct,
c.CommissionAmt,
c.TransactionCommissionAmt,
c.Description,
c.PrevFinalAmt,
c.PrevWrittenAmt,
c.ShortRateAmt,
c.CoinsurancePct,
c.LapseInd,
c.FutureStatusCd,
c.ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd,
c.ScheduledPremiumMod,
c.NumberOfEmployees,
c.NumberOfClass1Employees,
c.InsideLimit,
c.InsideDeductible,
c.OutsideLimit,
c.OutsideDeductible,
c.PapersKeptInCd,
c.DuplicateOffPremisesRecordsPct,
c.EDPEquipmentLimit,
c.EDPEquipmentInTransitLimit,
c.EDPDataLimit,
c.EDPMediaLimit,
c.EDPDataAndMediaInTransitLimit,
c.EDPBusinessIncomeLimit,
c.EDPExtraExpenseLimit,
c.FormType,
c.NumberOfDays,
c.NumberOfLocations,
c.CoverageType,
c.ClassificationRisk,
c.EQNumberOfStories,
c.EQRoofTankBuilding,
c.EQSublimitPercentage,
c.EQGradeDescription,
c.EQMasonryVeneerLimit,
c.EQBuildingConstruction,
c.Location,
c.StateRegistered,
c.OtherLocationDesc,
c.NumberOfPersons,
c.OrdOrLawPercentage,
c.FoodContaminationOption,
c.RefrigerationMaintenanceInd,
c.GURelatedExpensesLimit,
c.GUIncreasedLossCostPct,
c.GUExtPeriodOfRestoration,
c.RetroactiveDate,
c.Classification,
c.MasonryVeneerPct,
c.NumStories,
c.DeductibleTier,
c.RoofTank,
c.OptionalIncreasedDeductible,
c.NumLocations,
c.NumberOfTrusts,
c.NumberOfGolfCarts,
c.AsstCareNumOfFacilities,
c.RatingInd,
c.AddedViaHOCov,
c.RowId
FROM coverage c
join advrxxchangedbeans b
on c.Systemid=b.Systemid
and c.CmmContainer=b.CmmContainer
where c.CmmContainer in ('Application')
and concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt'
